        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>(b) the manufacture or repair of asbestos textiles or other articles containing or composed of asbestos;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>(c) the cleaning of any machinery or plant used in any foregoing operations and of any chambers, fixtures and appliances for the collection of asbestos dust;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>(d) substantial exposure to the dust arising from any of the foregoing operations.</td>
        </tr>
