            <td>(d) slate quarrying or the manufacturing of artefacts from slate. </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>(e) mining clay</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>(f) using siliceous materials as abrasives</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>(g) cutting stone</td>
        </tr>
